Class CourseList.CourseNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • CourseList.CourseNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    Enclosing class:
    CourseList

    class CourseList.CourseNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    inner class CourseNode will be used to create nodes for the CourseList. It implements the Cloneable interface allowing the addition of a clone() method. The class contains two private attributes, a Course object which will be stored in each node, and a CourseNode object used to for the CourseList pointer.
